### Requirements
- Accept file uploads via POST /upload
- Validate file type (images only: jpg, png, gif)
- Limit file size to 5MB
- Return file metadata on success
- See Example Usage section, to get more idea about Status codes and Response format

### Use Multer (Already Installed)
